  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Randomized, double-blind, parallel-group, multicenter study to assess efficacy, safety, and&#xD;
      tolerability of oral tropifexor &amp; licogliflozin combination therapy and each monotherapy,&#xD;
      compared with placebo for treatment of adult patients with nonalcoholic steatohepatitis&#xD;
      (NASH) and liver fibrosis&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Study to compare tropifexor and licogliflozin in combination and each monotherapy with&#xD;
      placebo for efficacy, safety, and tolerability in patients with NASH and fibrosis (stage 2 or&#xD;
      3) as per NASH CRN histological score.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
